### Auth Service - Health Check
GET {{auth_url}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Auth Service - Database Health (Smoke Test)
GET {{auth_url}}/health/db
Accept: application/json

### Auth Service - Create API Key (Admin)
POST {{auth_url}}/admin/keys
Authorization: Bearer {{master_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test Key"
}

### Auth Service - Validate Key (Requires Key from previous step)
GET {{auth_url}}/validate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_GENERATED_KEY_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Variables (Set your LoadBalancer IP or Localhost here)
@auth_url = http://localhost:8001
@master_key = mymasterkey
